id: pm-25d0
title: "GH-468: clarify or publish the pm SDK npm package coordinates (@unbrained/pm-sdk is 404)"
description: "Dogfood GH-468: package-author instructions say 'latest pm CLI and pm SDK' but npm view @unbrained/pm-sdk returns 404 — authors cannot tell whether the SDK is embedded in @unbrained/pm-cli, published elsewhere, or unpublished. Duplicate check: searched publish SDK npm package — pm-ds3b covers SDK reference docs, no item covers the package-coordinates decision."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: docs,gh-issue,packaging,sdk
created_at: "2026-07-06T21:08:40.224Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-07T02:53:36.031Z"
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: Canonical SDK import/package coordinates documented in pm contracts/help output and package-author docs; either @unbrained/pm-sdk is published/aliased or docs state explicitly the SDK ships inside @unbrained/pm-cli; a 'latest CLI/SDK package coordinates' section exists for agents
parent: pm-usfg
risk: medium
confidence: high
resolution: docs/SDK.md now clarifies that the SDK ships with @unbrained/pm-cli and is imported from @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk.
expected_result: Package authors know the correct npm package and import path for SDK usage.
actual_result: SDK docs updated and pm-changelog 2026.7.6 check confirmed CHANGELOG.md is unchanged.
